OL,6,FA man who shouted that he had a bomb
OL,7,Fand would blow up Newcastle Airport as
OL,8,Fpart of a video prank was described as
OL,9,Fan "idiot" as he was sentenced.
OL,11,FGarard Ndela tried to create fear he
OL,12,Fwas an Islamist terrorist by saying
OL,13,Fwords in Arabic before announcing that
OL,14,Fhe had an explosive device on the
OL,15,Fconcourse of the airport, Newcastle
OL,16,FCrown Court heard.
