OL,3,C'Self-entitled idiot' threatened to
OL,4,Cblow up airport for YouTube prank
OL,6,FHe was being filmed by accomplice,
OL,7,Fformer Newcastle Eagles academy
OL,8,Fbasketball player Andre Antonio and
OL,9,Fthey planned to post it on YouTube to
OL,10,Fgarner likes and "create humour".
OL,12,FDespite the alarming words, members of
OL,13,Fthe public and staff at the airport
OL,14,Fcan be seen in the video continuing
OL,15,Fabout their business and the pair did
OL,16,Fnot get the reaction they hoped for.
