OL,3,C'Self-entitled idiot' threatened to
OL,4,Cblow up airport for YouTube prank
OL,6,FIn the clip, Ndela emerged onto the
OL,7,Fconcourse, which was busy with staff
OL,8,Fand members of the public. After
OL,9,Fsaying something in Arabic, he
OL,10,Fannounced: "I'm at the airport right
OL,11,Fnow with a bomb. I'm about to blow the
OL,12,Fairport up with my bomb".
OL,14,FProsecutor Rachel Glover told
OL,15,FNewcastle Crown Court: "On being
OL,16,Fapproached by members of the public,
OL,17,Fhe repeated he had a bomb and there
OL,18,Fhad been no real reaction and he said
OL,19,Fhe wanted to be arrested."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
