OL,3,C'Self-entitled idiot' threatened to
OL,4,Cblow up airport for YouTube prank
OL,6,FShe added: "It's not in doubt members
OL,7,Fof the public would be fearful,
OL,8,Fespecially given the Arabic language
OL,9,Fused. The use of Arabic as a prelude
OL,10,Fto his announcement tends to instil
OL,11,Fhostility to Arabic speakers in the
OL,12,Fpublic."
OL,14,FNdela said he made a habit of such
OL,15,F"pranks" but there was no evidence on
OL,16,Fhis social media accounts of any other
OL,17,Fincidents which led to charges.
