OL,3,C'Self-entitled idiot' threatened to
OL,4,Cblow up airport for YouTube prank
OL,6,FJudge Amanda Rippon said: "He is a
OL,7,Fself-entitled idiot who thinks he is
OL,8,Fentitled to do what he want,
OL,9,Firrespective of who he upsets,
OL,10,Fintentionally using the Arabic
OL,11,Flanguage and all that fear that comes
OL,12,Ffrom people thinking an Islamist
OL,13,Fterrorist could blow up an airport.
OL,14,FThat was a deliberate attempt by him
OL,15,Fto cause fear and that's the most
OL,16,Fserious aspect of it."
