OL,6,FThe judge added she did not accept
OL,7,Fthat the 19-year-old would not
OL,8,Funderstand how serious terrorism is,
OL,9,Fand that it was "criminal" he planned
OL,10,Fto post the prank on YouTube for views
OL,11,Fand likes.
OL,13,FNdela, 20, of Ellison Villas,
OL,14,FGateshead, and Antonio, 21, of
OL,15,FChestnut Avenue, Cowgate, Newcastle,
OL,16,Fboth pleaded guilty to communicating
OL,17,Ffalse information.
