OL,6,FPassing sentence, Judge Rippon said
OL,7,Fshe was taking an "exceptional" course
OL,8,Fin suspending the sentences. She told
OL,9,Fthem: "It's the most moronic
OL,10,Fbehaviour. No one paid you any
OL,11,Fattention however you, Ndela, start
OL,12,Fyour bomb threat using Arabic on
OL,13,Fpurpose and it's plainly obvious you
OL,14,Fdid that because you knew that would
OL,15,Fbe what would get the most fearful and
OL,16,Fdistressing reaction."
