OL,6,F"It didn't cause an evacuation or
OL,7,Fdelay to any flights. He is sorry and
OL,8,Fdeeply apologetic."
OL,10,FJosh Normanton, for Antonio, said he
OL,11,Fhad told Ndela "don't do it" in the
OL,12,Flead up to the offence. Mr Normanton
OL,13,Fadded: "it was a wholly stupid venture
OL,14,Fbased on a cultural shift towards
OL,15,Fcertain immoral behaviour that's seen
OL,16,Fas acceptable by people on YouTube and
OL,17,FTikTok."
